---
title: Cheddar-Crusted Chicken Thighs with Sweet Potato Mash and Green Beans
description: Tonight's menu features cheddar-crusted chicken, sweet potato mash and roasted green beans. The best part? Everything comes together in 30 minutes! Talk about a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cuisses-de-poulet-en-croute-de-cheddar-519f9023.jpg
